channel.title: Earn some cash online
channel.description: Hey guys, I don't want to get really personal but my mom is kinda doing her own thing atm, she doesn't have much money so.. If I want to get something I'm going to have to use my own money for it.. I was just wondering if any of you know a way to make some good cash online. I was looking into making youtube videos but I don't have a mic to talk into (unless turtle beaches work.. if someone could tell me if I can use them to make commentaries that would be great) so that isn't really going to work. Ebay? I don't have much of anything to sell on Ebay besides a few skateboards. I was going to and probably still am going to develop a RSPS and maybe make a couple bucks out of that. The real problem here is I really don't know how to make money.. I can't really find a good job considering I am 14. I am just looking for a good way to make a few bucks online. Someone said something about making an iPhone app and I can get tons of cash for that.. I might look into this but I really don't know how. Could someone just give any suggestions on making cash online.
